    <item>
      <title>关税生效前，洛杉矶港进口量持续激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/port-of-los-angeles-sees-sustained-import-surge-ahead-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于企业在潜在的关税上调之前进口货物，并试图避免备用港口出现与劳工相关的中断，美国最繁忙的海上贸易综合体上个月的进口量继续接近创纪录的水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/port-of-los-angeles-sees-sustained-import-surge-ahead-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 18:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
